headline: Garmin Ltd. schedules first quarter 2025 earnings call
summary: Garmin Ltd. (NYSE: GRMN) invites shareholders and investors to listen to its first quarter 2025 earnings conference call on Wednesday, April 30, 2025, at 10:30 a.m. EDT, with executives of Garmin. The call will be held in conjunction with the company's earnings release, which will be distributed prior to market open on April 30, 2025.
